{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Intl.NumberFormat.supportedLocalesOf()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat/supportedLocalesOf","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard built-in objects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl\"><code>Intl</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>プロパティ</strong></a><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/@@toStringTag\"><code>Intl[@@toStringTag]</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>メソッド</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/getCanonicalLocales\"><code>Intl.getCanonicalLocales()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/supportedValuesOf\"><code>Intl.supportedValuesOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>関連するページ</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/Collator\"><code>Intl.Collator</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.DateTimeFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/ListFormat\"><code>Intl.ListFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat\"><code>Intl.NumberFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/PluralRules\"><code>Intl.PluralRules</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/RelativeTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.RelativeTimeFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/Segmenter\"><code>Intl.Segmenter</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong>継承</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>プロパティ</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>メソッド</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>Intl.ListFormat.supportedLocalesOf()</code></strong> メソッドは、ランタイムの既定のロケールで代替する必要なく数値の書式で対応されているものを含む配列を返します。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect1\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"410\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/intl-numberformat-prototype-supportedlocalesof.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">Intl.NumberFormat.supportedLocalesOf(<var>locales</var>[, <var>options</var>])</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"locales\"><code><var>locales</var></code></dt>\n <dd>BCP 47 言語タグを持つ文字列、またはそのような文字列の配列です。 <code>locales</code> 引数の一般的な形式については、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl#%E3%83%AD%E3%82%B1%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AB%E3%81%AE%E8%AD%98%E5%88%A5%E3%81%A8%E3%83%8D%E3%82%B4%E3%82%B7%E3%82%A8%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%B3\">Intl のページ</a>を参照してください。</dd>\n <dt id=\"options\"><code><var>options</var></code></dt>\n <dd>\n <p>省略可能です。以下のプロパティを持つことがあるオブジェクトです。</p>\n\n <dl>\n  <dt id=\"localematcher\"><code>localeMatcher</code></dt>\n  <dd>使用するロケールの一致アルゴリズムです。指定可能な値は <code>lookup</code> および <code>best fit</code> で、既定値は <code>best fit</code> です。このオプションの詳細は、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl#locale_negotiation\">Intl のページ</a>を参照してください。</dd>\n </dl>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>指定したロケールタグのサブセットを表す文字列の配列で、ランタイムの既定のロケールで代替する必要なく数値の書式で対応されているものを含みます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"解説","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>locales</code> で提供されている言語タグのサブセットを含む配列を返します。返される言語タグは、ランタイムが数値のロケールに対応しているもので、使用しているロケール照合アルゴリズムで一致しているとみなされているものです。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"using_supportedlocalesof","title":"supportedLocalesOf() の使用","isH3":true,"content":"<p>数値の書式でインドネシア語とドイツ語に対応しており、バリ語に対応していないランタイムを想定すると、 <code>supportedLocalesOf</code> はインドネシア語とドイツ語の言語タグを変更せずに返しますが、 <code>pinyin</code> の照合は数値の書式には関係なく、インドネシア語でも使用されません。ここでの <code>lookup</code> アルゴリズムの仕様に注意してください — バリ語話者のほとんどはインドネシア語も理解しているので、 <code>best fit</code> のマッチャーはインドネシア語がバリ語に適切に一致すると判断し、バリ語の言語タグも返すかもしれません。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> locales <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'ban'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'id-u-co-pinyin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'de-ID'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> options <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">localeMatcher</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'lookup'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NumberFormat<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">supportedLocalesOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>locales<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">join</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">', '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// → \"id-u-co-pinyin, de-ID\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma402/#sec-intl.numberformat.supportedlocalesof\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript Internationalization API (ECMA-402)<br><small lang=\"ja\">Intl.NumberFormat.supportedLocalesOf の定義</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Intl.NumberFormat.supportedLocalesOf","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat/supportedLocalesOf/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat\"><code>Intl.NumberFormat</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"解説","id":"description"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Intl.ListFormat.supportedLocalesOf() メソッドは、ランタイムの既定のロケールで代替する必要なく数値の書式で対応されているものを含む配列を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Intl.NumberFormat.supportedLocalesOf()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Intl.NumberFormat.supportedLocalesOf()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Intl.NumberFormat.supportedLocalesOf()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Intl.NumberFormat.supportedLocalesOf()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/intl/numberformat/supportedlocalesof","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/intl/numberformat/supportedlocalesof/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript リファレンス"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"標準組み込みオブジェクト"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl","title":"Intl"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat","title":"Intl.NumberFormat"},{"uri":"/ja/d